title: Matthijs Hardijk
text:
Matthijs Hardijk (born 25 December 1997) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="ACV%20Assen">ACV Assen</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> debut for <a href="Jong%20AZ">Jong AZ</a> on 18 August 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Den%20Bosch">FC Den Bosch</a>.
